response.original_title: I Was A Shemale For The FBI
response.overview: The F.B.I. is looking for new recruits to go undercover, and what better recruit than to hire Summer St. Cerly. The best of both worlds who can go under anyone's covers to fuck pertinent information from out of them, and set up the "sting" for the FBI to storm in the room and make the arrest; also starring; Chaz Holderman, Chris Parker, Dana Douglas, Heather Holmes, and Michael Ryan.
